{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "eleave-login-2024",
        "name": "eLeave Login API",
        "description": "API for eLeave Login - Authentication Service\n\n## Features\n- **Authentication**: Multiple authentication strategies (Local, AD, Email)\n- **User Management**: Full CRUD operations for users\n- **Encryption Utilities**: SHA256 and AES encryption/decryption\n\n## Pre-request Scripts\n- All authentication requests automatically encode passwords with base64 (atob format expected by API)\n- All protected endpoints check for valid access token\n- Encryption tests chain together (encrypt → verify, encrypt → decrypt)\n\n## Post-response Scripts\n- Login responses automatically extract and store access tokens\n- Encryption tests verify results and store encrypted values for subsequent tests\n- User management responses log results for debugging\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `base_url`: API base URL (default: http://localhost:3003)\n- `access_token`: JWT token for authenticated requests\n- `test_password`: Password for encryption tests\n- `aes_key`: AES encryption key (default: 'secret key 122')",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Authentication",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Login Local",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login/local",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "login",
                                "local"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Login with local database authentication",
                        "preRequestScript": "// Encode password with atob (base64) as expected by the API\n// In production, you would decode this on the client side\n// The API expects base64 encoded password\nvar password = pm.environment.get('password') || 'password';\nvar encodedPassword = btoa(password);\n\n// Update the request body with encoded password\nvar body = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);\nbody.password = encodedPassword;\npm.request.body.raw = JSON.stringify(body);",
                        "script": {
                            "id": "login-local-script",
                            "exec": [
                                "if (pm.response.successful) {",
                                "    var response = pm.response.json();",
                                "    if (response.access_token) {",
                                "        pm.environment.set('access_token', response.access_token);",
                                "        console.log('Login successful. Token:', response.access_token);",
                                "    } else {",
                                "        console.log('Login failed. No token received.');",
                                "    }",
                                "} else {",
                                "    console.log('Login failed. Status:', pm.response.code);",
                                "}"
                            ],
                            "type": "text"
                        }
                    }
                },
